---
type: structured
description: Context prompt for screenplay review providing outline, characters, style guidelines, and iteration state
---
{# Variables: age_range, page_outline, characters, illustration_style, shot_style_spec, previous_checklist, current_iteration, max_iterations #}

{% block base_instruction %}
Target audience age range: {{ age_range }}

Page Outline:
{{ page_outline }}

Characters:
{{ characters }}

SHOT STYLE GUIDELINES ({{ illustration_style }} style):
{{ shot_style_spec }}

Previous Checklist (completed=true items are past decisions — DO NOT reverse them):
{{ previous_checklist }}

Critic Iteration: {{ current_iteration }} of {{ max_iterations }}
WIND-DOWN: When current_iteration exceeds half of max_iterations, downgrade all remaining P1 items to P2. Focus only on P0 blockers.
{% endblock %}
